author: Li Yunbing
notes: Li Yunbing [李云兵]. 2005. A Study of Bugeng (Bugan) [布赓语研究]. Beijing: Minzu University.This variety of Bugan is that of Manlong 曼龙, Haizi Village 海子村, Jijie Township 鸡街乡 (pronounced Jigai in the local Southwestern Mandarin dialect), Xichou County, Yunnan, China. It differs somewhat from the Bugan variety recorded by Li Jinfang in Nala 那腊, Guangnan County.Subscript tildes signify tenseness.
